Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
I belive it is a good thing for freshman to live on campus for the first year. Because when they first come to the school, they are unfamilar with everything and everybody. If they live in a dorm, they will have opportunity to make friends and get to know the school together.